  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK754">
<l>aṟaṉīṉu miṉpamu mīṉun tiṟaṉaṟintu</l>
<l>tītiṉṟi vanta poruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth acquired with a knowledge of the proper means and without foul practices will yield virtue and happiness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
